    <h3>Jessic Shi</h3>
    <div class='bio'>
      <p>
        Jessica Shi is a spine therapist and the owner of Tree of Life Yoga and Spine Therapy in Emeryville, California. She comes from a family of back pain sufferers, and has first hand experience with a variety of spine ailments, including: stenosis, scoliosis, disc diseases and sciatica. She rehabilitated her own spine injuries through various forms of manual therapy, and continues to share her practice with her clients.
      </p>
      <p>
        Jessica's approach is unique and catered to each individual. It is deeply rooted in the scientific principles of anatomy and kinesiology, and incorporates energetic and breath work that is more intuitive and psychosomatic. No two bodies are alike, even if the patterns of pain are similar. She adapts her work according to each client's specific needs and body type, and empowers her clients to become more aware of their own.
      </p>
    </div>
