      <span class='contact-info'>Contact Jessica</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='teacher'>
    <%= image_tag('Vita.png', id: 'teacher-img') %>
    <h3>Vita Zus Burwell</h3>
    <div class='bio'>
      <p>
        Vita Zus Burwell has been working and studying with Jessica Shi at Tree of Life since early 2013. Body awareness and movement has always been part of her life: gymnastics, long distance running, eleven years of dance with ballet foundation, eight years of yoga practice.
      </p>
      <p>
        Vita believes in the interconnected body-mind system approach to health and happiness: when our physical bodies are in optimal health and alignment, the overall quality of life is uplifted. Having trained and worked with various bodywork professionals and therapists, she brings her rich background into her work. She loves teaching her clients to move safely, access deep and subtle sensations, and understand the cause-effect of their habitual patterns.
      </p>
    </div>
